high_descs: Turn around and walk to stand in front of the sink.
Pick the apple up from out of the sink.
Go to the right and then the right again to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the apple up.
Go to the left, and then the left again to stand facing the sink.
Put the apple down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.

high_descs: MOve to kitchen sink to the left of the fridge on the other side of the island.
Pick up apple from inside the sink.
Move to the fridge to the right of you to the left of the island.
Place apple inside and chill for a moment before removing and closing the door.
Move to sink to the left of you in front of the window.
Place apple inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right to go towards the wall then back around to go past the island. Walk to the counter and make a left and then face the sink.
Take the apple from the sink.
Go to the right with the apple and then make another right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the apple on the shelf next to the potato. Shut the door and after a few seconds open it and take the apple back out.
Turn left to go back towards the counter then make another left and a right to face the sink.
Put the apple back in the sink in front of the drain.
anns.task_desc: To move the apple to the fridge finally back to the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, walk past the island, turn left, turn to face sink.
Take the apple from the sink.
Turn right, turn right and walk halfway along the island, turn to face refrigerator.
Put apple in refrigerator, take apple out of refrigerator.
Turn left, turn right, turn to face sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the sink.
